snippet.title: Alarm for Cobra 11 Vol. 2 - Hot Pursuit - Gameplay ( terrible racer ) PS2 HD
snippet.description:
larm For Cobra 11 Vol.2 - Hot Pursuit is the 2nd of 2 games released for the PS2 and is a repackaged, re-skinned and slightly altered version of the racing game originally released as London Racer World Challenge. 

Developed by Davilex and published by Midas Interactive Entertainment, which was released in Europe only in 2005. 

Alarm für Cobra 11 – Die Autobahnpolizei is a long-running, German television series broadcast in countries worldwide under different names. 

Davilex Releases : 

A2 Racer-serie
London Racer-serie
Autobahn Racer-serie
Paris-Marseille Racing-serie
Europe Racer
USA Racer
Grachtenracer
Vakantie Racer
Amsterdam Taxi Madness
